OL,7,FAppearing at the Afghanistan Inquiry
OL,8,FJohnny Mercer refused to reveal names
OL,9,Fof officers who told him of claims
OL,10,Funarmed Afghans had been shot by
OL,11,FBritish forces
OL,13,FThe Veterans' Minister Johnny Mercer
OL,14,Fhas said serving army officers told
OL,15,Fhim unarmed Afghans were shot by UK
OL,16,Fspecial forces in Afghanistan.
