OL,7,FMr Mercer was giving evidence to the
OL,8,FAfghanistan inquiry, which is looking
OL,9,Fat killings of unarmed civilians by UK
OL,10,Fspecial forces during night raids
OL,11,Fthroughout the war, from mid-2010 to
OL,12,Fmid-2013.
OL,14,FHe told the public inquiry he was
OL,15,F"desperate" to disprove a cover-up of
OL,16,Falleged murders by UK special forces
OL,17,Fin the war-torn nation but was
OL,18,F"unable" to do so.
