OL,7,FThe veterans' minister is known for
OL,8,Fhis opposition to false allegations
OL,9,Fagainst UK forces, particularly in
OL,10,FIraq.
OL,12,FBut during his campaign against
OL,13,Finaccurate claims, he says he was told
OL,14,Fby a friend and serving military
OL,15,Fofficer not to dig too far.
OL,17,FHe said they discussed there were
OL,18,Fserious allegations against special
OL,19,Fforces in Afghanistan which involved
OL,20,F"the killing of individuals who pose
OL,21,Fno threat".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/12
