OL,7,FMr Mercer told the inquiry he "did not
OL,8,Fbelieve" the director of special
OL,9,Fforces and the chief of general staff
OL,10,Fwhen they told him there was no
OL,11,Fevidence of extra-judicial killings.
OL,13,FAfter his conversations with the pair,
OL,14,Fhe said he told then-defence secretary
OL,15,FBen Wallace "something stinks".
OL,17,FMr Mercer says he was unable to
OL,18,Fdisprove a cover-up of the alleged
OL,19,Fmurders.
