OL,7,F"I have been desperate for some sort
OL,8,Fof evidence to disprove these
OL,9,Fallegations because I don't want to
OL,10,Fbelieve them, I don't want to believe
OL,11,Fthem from that unit.
OL,13,F"I have friends who were killed in
OL,14,Foperations, I have friends who were
OL,15,Fnever the same person again after
OL,16,FAfghanistan.
OL,18,F"And I don't want to believe it, but
OL,19,Fat every stage I have tried to find
OL,20,Fsomething to disprove these
OL,21,Fallegations but I have been unable to."
