OL,7,FITV News' Political Correspondent Carl
OL,8,FDinnen was following the inquiry.
OL,10,FThe veterans' minister refused to give
OL,11,Fthe names of his sources when asked by
OL,12,FOliver Glasgow KC.
OL,14,F"I am not prepared to burn them", he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FMr Glasgow put it to him that failing
OL,18,Fto provide the names of those who told
OL,19,Fhim the information would
OL,20,F"considerably hamper" the inquiry's
OL,21,Fwork.
