OL,7,FMr Mercer replied: "The one thing you
OL,8,Fcan hold on to is your integrity and I
OL,9,Fwill be doing that with these
OL,10,Findividuals."
OL,12,FLawyers representing the 11 bereaved
OL,13,Ffamilies at the inquiry said "Johnny
OL,14,FMercer's candid testimony lays bare
OL,15,Fthe depth of concern that has existed
OL,16,Ffor years within the army and at the
OL,17,Fhighest levels of government that UK
OL,18,FSpecial Forces were carrying out extra
OL,19,Fjudicial killings in Afghanistan."
